                                    oc:codeContent """ ## Architecture
 ...

+## Commands
+
+| Command | Purpose |
+|---------|---------|
+| `npm run dev` | Dev server with HMR |
+| `npm run build` | Production build |
+| `npm test` | Run test suite |
""" ;
                                    oc:codeLanguage "diff" ;
